text: Gymnothorax eurygnathos is a moray eel found in the eastern central Pacific Ocean, around the Gulf of California.Gymnothorax eurygnathos at www.fishbase.org. It was first named by Eugenia B. Böhlke in 2001. ==References== ==External links== * Gymnothorax eurygnathos, a new moray from the Gulf of California (Anguilliformes: Muraenidae). eurygnathos Category:Fish described in 2001
